<plot>One man's journey from child soldier to national hero. As a young boy, Aki Ra was groomed to be an instrument of war by the Khmer Rouge regime. In his adult life, Aki Ra has worked to combat the violence in which he once took part by removing what he can of the six million landmines that still mar Cambodia's countryside.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?664482</url></doc>
